@yxieca I made an equivalent change for `202211` and `master`.
This change is directly targeting 202205 because it performs some submodule updates to our platform drivers.
AFAIK submodules updates are not easy to cherry-pick hence the reason I made individual PRs for each branch.

the main problem is that with this revert we are missing a lot of changes coming from swss-common which are needed just because debug image is not available.
@lguohan  is this the right approach?
what is the offended commit that cause it? maybe that one can be reverted on swss-common so we can have the rest in master?
